今日都投咗兩次<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/PolicePublicPage?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;language=en&amp;fontSize=100&amp;homepage=C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2FPolicePublicPage%3Freport%3DCMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR%26language%3Den%26fontSize%3D100%26homepage%3DC&d=%2FodnS2mEGvHoUZPzyf%2FmNdTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=506ad4cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/PolicePublicPage?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;language=en&amp;fontSize=100&amp;homepage=C</a>"},{"pid":"40c0e97a7ed624ba97c67d3d063bfe55669c489d","tid":1203934,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:52:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6d8fd6f08a95900e176951186b2a5e2c85124f0","tid":1203934,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"拍片都驚俾人搶電話,<br />\n<br />\n先大叫搵多D人睇實,<br />\n<br />\n去人多既地方搜, 廢時俾人濫用私刑,<br />\n<br />\n加俾群眾壓力佢, 等多D人知道佢地無啦啦搜9人, 濫權"},{"pid":"c3da7f933a031afa2d37441d1de5b8db197fff61","tid":1203934,"uid":84367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:55:19.000Z","msg":"第232章 《警隊條例》<br />\n54.截停、扣留及搜查的權力<br />\n(1)警務人員如在任何街道或其他公眾地方、或於任何船隻或交通工具上，不論日夜任何時間，發現任何人行動可疑，該警務人員採取以下行動，乃屬合法 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)截停該人以要求他出示身分證明文件供該警務人員查閱；<br />\n(b)扣留該人一段合理期間，在該期間內由該警務人員查究該人是否涉嫌在任何時候犯了任何罪行；及<br />\n(c)如該警務人員認為以下行動乃屬必需 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n   <span style=\"color: red;\"> (i)向該人搜查任何可能對該警務人員構成危險的東西；及<br />\n    (ii)扣留該人一段為作出該項搜查而合理需要的期間。</span><br />\n<br />\n憲法及《基本法》<br />\n第三章: 居民的基本權利和義務<br />\n第二十八條<br />\n香港居民的人身自由不受侵犯。<br />\n<br />\n香港居民不受任意或非法逮捕、拘留、監禁。禁止任意或非法搜查居民的身體、<span style=\"color: red;\">剝奪或限制居民的人身自由</span>。禁止對居民施行酷刑、任意或非法剝奪居民的生命。<br />\n<br />\n記得：<br />\n查問警員編號<br />\n警員無權隨意搜身<br />\n查問合理懷疑<br />\n被查完身份證詢問自己是否可以離開<br />\n拍片保護自己<br />\n警員無權查看市民電話，有搜查令先可以<br />\n警員無權要市民罰企"},{"pid":"2455971e614c49d98082abc4137b407ecaaccb98","tid":1203934,"uid":96896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"佢哋可以咁大膽搜 擺到明有上頭order 就算投訴根本冇用"},{"pid":"811e2fb48383b9e60fbf663f5ae03f2012fafce8","tid":1203934,"uid":69681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"麻煩各位巴絲幫手backup啲片同相 包括直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4387a9b113c74a1d60dc3194b5fa7ccbacbbae57","tid":1203934,"uid":240976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592d592c0c4ed8f582aaba28757351ffe02bb325","tid":1203934,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"唔係重點，但阻阻大家，有緣見到CCTVB做直播/收音就大嗌或自製banner<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n嗌咩唔係重點，齊心屌鳩TVB<br />\n目的係影響tvb收音，拍攝緊嘅畫面<br />\n過往經驗，佢做live無得cut，直上電視，但新聞時段就會cut晒呢啲畫面/收音，令佢無嘢播都好<br />\n<br />\n橫掂TVB妓者都係鳩噏<br />\n血債血償，清鳩tvb袋<br />\n<br />\n有片，例子參考 : <br />\n[呼籲]有緣見到CCTVB，大家要識做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1202083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1202083</a>"},{"pid":"894f69bb0466a4ad475223b5651e650f1e1d5c3f","tid":1203934,"uid":258785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dba83443a765ae9acacfea031dd691655021912","tid":1203934,"uid":69064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0df968d8f7100208aa1c8324beed1924718359bc","tid":1203934,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />